high_descs: Walk to the left side of the desk in front of you.
Pick up the bowl from the desk.
Turn right and walk in front of the lamp that is on the desk to the left of the bed.
anns.task_desc: Examine a bowl by the light of a desk lamp.

high_descs: Walk around to the front of the desk by the chair.
Pick up the bowl that is closest to the window.
Turn right and walk towards the bed, turn left and walk to the other desk, then turn to face it.
Turn on the lamp on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the lamp while holding a bowl.

high_descs: Walk to the window and face the desk.
Pick up the bowl on the desk.
Walk to the second desk on the other side of the room.
anns.task_desc: Examine a bowl by the lamp.
